en:
60 spacious apartments equipped with kitchenette, HD TV, free Wifi, safe, hair dryer, air conditioning, in a quiet and green setting 800 m from the beach of Cabourg.
The Kyriad Prestige residence also offers a relaxation area, a swimming pool with terrace, a whirlpool, a hammam and a private parking lot.
